UML:TaggedValue.value: This package defines the requirements of the FSDF PlaceNames Theme Conceptual model

UML:ClassifierRole.name: Implementable as lossless common data transfer

UML:TaggedValue.value: The FSDF PlaceName theme recognises that place names need to support unambiguous identification, even though names themselves may be re-used. The ISO 19112 Spatial Referencing by Identifier model addresses these concerns. This alignment implies that instances of FSDF placenames can be traced to a source dataset (a Gazetteer).
